				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-H%C3%A0-Ninh-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n/poem-wW--Ls6Jp03hc-G-Bety4A">Điếu Hà Ninh tổng đốc Hoàng đại nhân - 吊河寧總督黃大人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/Ho%E1%BA%A3-l%C3%B4-ti%E1%BB%81n-to%E1%BA%A1/poem-YNCtOhujBsM_FtdygiOCMA">Hoả lô tiền toạ - 火爐前坐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-zIVIj-WVByE189TCoytv8g">Lý Quần Ngọc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/H%E1%BB%B1u-th%C3%B9-Ph%C3%B3-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9-th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-cwTDzDI3TeY5FTwFl3Tg5Q">Hựu thù Phó xử sĩ thứ vận - 又酬傅處士次韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A1t-%C4%90%C3%B4-L%E1%BA%A1t/Kh%C3%AA-h%C3%A0nh-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-ng%E1%BA%A1n-giai-ph%C3%B9-dung-qu%E1%BA%BF-hoa-d%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%89-to%E1%BA%A1i-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BB%AD-thi/poem-dh-sgOE8sj_wFTJsIRuiUA">Khê hành lưỡng ngạn giai phù dung quế hoa dư hỉ toại phú thử thi - 溪行兩岸皆芙蓉桂花余喜遂賦此詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A1t-%C4%90%C3%B4-L%E1%BA%A1t/author-o6P2TdkwVUJwiHY0ASq8kw">Tát Đô Lạt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/Kinh-Ch%C3%A2u-h%E1%BA%ADu-kh%E1%BB%95-tuy%E1%BA%BFt-d%E1%BA%ABn/poem-u06Cqs7u1F0YDvHylKIiyA">Kinh Châu hậu khổ tuyết dẫn - 荊州後苦雪引</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZqGaWwKOrJXGaqhA3jlDaw">Viên Hoằng Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Y2Apy7vZ7BJ3xIXQl4vYRg">Nhập trạch kỳ 2 - 入宅其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/S%C6%A1n-H%E1%BA%A3i-quan/poem-b1qPILLyhjokTIDBUXckBA">Sơn Hải quan - 山海關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Jg_4_inbL47zGqzn3fJTrw">Lạc Thành Tương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/T%E1%BB%8Bch-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-ctvl16B1W_mPEBeB7nJdBg">Tịch dương - 夕陽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1m-C%C3%B4ng-quy-Tung-S%C6%A1n-Long-%C4%90%C3%A0m-t%E1%BB%B1-t%C3%A1ng-b%E1%BA%A3n-s%C6%B0/poem-r0tF2LPxwYqCfwwJ_meS1Q">Tống Đạm Công quy Tung Sơn Long Đàm tự táng bản sư - 送澹公歸嵩山龍潭寺葬本師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-ujv3_N4k0KkIvWqK4PUlgw">Dương Cự Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-An-Trinh/V%C4%83n-l%C3%A2n-gia-l%C3%BD-tranh/poem-1nPi_YLwNjj6jqJJ5OtTPg">Văn lân gia lý tranh - 聞鄰家理箏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-An-Trinh/author-d-FDjEupVCgpsc1eaacNvg">Từ An Trinh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
